.TH "zynqmp_dp_set_format" 9 "zynqmp_dp_set_format" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
zynqmp_dp_set_format \- Set the input format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" zynqmp_dp_set_format
.BI "(struct zynqmp_dp *dp "  ","
.BI "enum zynqmp_dpsub_format format "  ","
.BI "unsigned int bpc "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dp" 12
DisplayPort IP core structure
.IP "format" 12
input format
.IP "bpc" 12
bits per component
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update misc register values based on input \fIformat\fP and \fIbpc\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or -EINVAL.
